data.description: Welcome to this 2 bedroom / 2 bathroom home located in the vibrant neighborhood of Uptown Yucaipa! Upon entry through the charming covered front porch, step inside to the large open-concept living and dining room space. Down the hall is the primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom, as well as the secondary bedroom and bathroom. Adjacent to the dining room is the kitchen with space for a breakfast nook. The laundry room leads into the spacious sunroom which offers a wonderful addition of living space. The entire interior of the home has been freshly painted and brand new carpet installed in both bedrooms. Situated on a sizable lot, the backyard is the perfect space to entertain, complete with artificial turf and mature walnut, peach, plum, and almond trees. There is plenty of parking with the long driveway and detached garage. Inside of the garage is a small room that would be a great space for a private home office. Additional features of the home include a brand new water heater and upgraded lighting and ceiling fan fixtures throughout. Refrigerator conveniently included! Located right around the corner from Yucaipa Blvd, there are so many local amenities to enjoy, such as shopping, restaurants, events at the Yucaipa Performing Arts Center, and much more! Don't miss the opportunity to make this perfectly located home yours!
